<P>__{wes{cont)}
<D>__{they're surrendering to a news crew. you believe that?}
<A>__{jaeger tosses his hands in the air in defeat.}
<C>__{jaeger}
<D>__{that's it. it's over. eighteen hours into the war and it's over.}
