<D>__{it's real. i'm telling you, it's real.}
<C>__{wes}
<D>__{so you just want to cross into hostile territory in the middle of a war on a wild goose chase? it's crazy. tell him it's crazy, epps.}
<A>__{epps thinks. he doesn't say nuthin', just thinks. it's the thinking that makes wes nervous.}
<C>__{wes}
<D>__{epps, tell him.}
<A>__{epps gets a little more thinking in. wes sees which way this is going.}
